OL,3,CGerman bunker at Jersey beach
OL,4,Cvandalised with graffiti
OL,6,FVandals have 'desecrated' a German
OL,7,Fbunker at St Brelade's bay by spraying
OL,8,Fit with graffiti says the Parish
OL,9,FConstable.
OL,11,FThe wall is at the end of the walkway
OL,12,Fthat connects St Brelade's bay before
OL,13,Fit goes over the hill to Ouaisne beach.
OL,15,FConstable Mike Jackson said: "Having
OL,16,Fhad sight of the graffiti on the
OL,17,Fconcrete German bunkers it is sad that
OL,18,Fas historic monuments they've been
OL,19,Fdesecrated."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/2
