OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1777406752
OL,3,CGerman bunker at Jersey beach
OL,4,Cvandalised with graffiti
OL,6,FHe added: "Whilst some might suggest
OL,7,Fthat the artwork could be perceived as
OL,8,Fbeing of a reasonable standard as far
OL,9,Fas graffiti goes, it's not something I
OL,10,Fcan condone and would discourage the
OL,11,Fartists from doing this as it is a
OL,12,Fcriminal offence."
OL,14,FThere was mixed reaction from those at
OL,15,Fthe beach, with some saying it
OL,16,F'brightens up' the area, whilst others
OL,17,Fsaying although 'not offensive' it
OL,18,Fisn't in keeping with area.
